#howitworks.block.content
 .section.has-text-centered
  .title How it works
  .subtitle The power of Markdown, Frontmatter and Obsidian
  video(controls='' width='100%' autoplay='' loop='')
    source(src='{{url_for("static", path="webm/20240123-demo.webm")}}' type='video/webm' loop="true")

 .column.is-6.is-offset-3
  .media
    figure.media-left.ml-2
      p.image.is-128x128
        img(src='{{url_for("static", path="img/howto/plugin-configuration.png")}}').is-rounded
    .media-content
      .content
        .title.is-5.mb-1
          strong Configure the Plugin
        p After installing the plugin, a single click in the plugin's settings is all it takes to link your Relay.md account in Obsidian. No further configuration is required. It couldn't be easier to set up.

  .media
    figure.media-left.ml-2
      p.image.is-128x128
        img(src='{{url_for("static", path="img/howto/frontmatter.png")}}').is-rounded
    .media-content
      .content
        .title.is-5.mb-1
          strong Add properties to your document
        p Use the frontmatter key&nbsp;
          span.tag.is-dark
            tt relay-to
          | &nbsp;to list individual recipients or
          | entire teams with a subject. &nbsp;
          a(href="{{url_for('relay_basics')}}") Learn more.

  .media
    figure.media-left.ml-2
      p.image.is-128x128
        img(src='{{url_for("static", path="img/howto/downloaded-articles-in-base-folder.png")}}').is-rounded
    .media-content
      .content
        .title.is-5.mb-1
          strong Receive your documents
        p You will automatically receive shared documents, sorted into corresponding teams and subjects. Each document contains a unique identifier that allows the plugin to locate the document anywhere in your vault for updates. We recommend that you move the documents you receive into your usual hierarchy.

  .media
    figure.media-left.ml-2
      p.image.is-128x128
        img(src='{{url_for("static", path="img/howto/document-search.png")}}').is-rounded
    .media-content
      .content
        .title.is-5.mb-1
          strong Access documents online
        p Public documents can be accessed through the website using the unique document ID. Simply share the ID and people can read the document by searching online.

  .media
    figure.media-left.ml-2
      p.image.is-128x128
        img(src='{{url_for("static", path="img/howto/api.png")}}').is-rounded
    .media-content
      .content
        .title.is-5.mb-1
          strong Developer Access
        p You can build your own applications using our API at&nbsp;
          a(href='https://api.relay.md/docs') api.relay.md
          | . Feel free to build your own note taking app integration, or&nbsp;
          a(href="{{url_for('contact')}}") contact us using
          | &nbsp;for assistance.
